WEBVTT

00:00:00.524 --> 00:00:01.844
Došla sam danas ovde

00:00:01.844 --> 00:00:04.151
da pričamo o problemu.

00:00:04.151 --> 00:00:07.678
To je veoma jednostavan
ali razoran problem,

00:00:07.678 --> 00:00:09.623
koji je prisutan širom planete

00:00:09.623 --> 00:00:12.536
i koji pogađa sve nas.

00:00:12.536 --> 00:00:14.621
Problem su

00:00:14.621 --> 00:00:17.346
anonimne kompanije.

00:00:17.346 --> 00:00:19.536
Zvuči kao zaista suvoparan
i tehnički termin,

00:00:19.536 --> 00:00:20.492
zar ne?

00:00:20.492 --> 00:00:22.994
Ali anonimne kompanije otežavaju

00:00:22.994 --> 00:00:25.546
i ponekad čine nemogućim

00:00:25.546 --> 00:00:27.395
da se otkrije

00:00:27.395 --> 00:00:30.394
osoba koja je zapravo odgovorna